## Salmon_SyS_Dashboard ###

This code was developed as a prototype to explore concepts for a potential mortality monitoring dashboard in salmon farming.
Active development was paused.

The script 'data_salmonSyS.r' is not included due to data confidentiality.
A example dataset has been created with variables that appear in data_salmon_SyS, 
see data_dashboard_Salmon_SyS_demo.R for running dashboard_Salmon_SyS_demo.R 

This work has received funding from the European Union’s
Horizon 2020 Research and Innovation Programme under
the DECIDE-Project (grant agreement no. 101000494).
